{"id": 3030, "genre": 1001, "title": "「工作」这种生活状态都给你带来了哪些潜移默化的影响？", "description": "工作不仅改变了我们的观念和行为，还成为了一种「生活方式」。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 1727, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191015215438Ha26lkYzu53vLCQn.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-16T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 348416, "content": "工作啊，无非就是把我变成了一个深居简出的山顶洞人（深居六楼无电梯）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267956}, {"id": 348417, "content": "感觉我好累啊，除了睡觉之外，不是在上班，就是在去上班的路上...... ​​​​", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945960}, {"id": 348673, "content": "手机长时间震动、电话下意识录音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402590}, {"id": 348420, "content": "找不到工作和生活间的平衡点！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713728}, {"id": 348421, "content": "对自我价值与这份工作是否存在实际意义感到怀疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455119}, {"id": 348422, "content": "工作中，找不到自己的价值高。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667278}, {"id": 348423, "content": "深切体会到“时间是挤出来的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660780}, {"id": 348424, "content": "感觉没有手机就活不下去 这个事情没有你做就不行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609710}, {"id": 348425, "content": "还没工作的我瑟瑟发抖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 348427, "content": "明白了金钱和成就能带来快乐，但金钱与成就无法带来全部快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662211}, {"id": 348683, "content": "决定让（工作之外的）生活每天都梦寐以求", "image": "img/option/option/201910220845122MDFWw6jVyIJRdk8.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613131}, {"id": 348939, "content": "和小时候渴望长大后的样子越来越远", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324065}, {"id": 348430, "content": "要命的生物钟，工作以后，很少再睡懒觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 348436, "content": "可以卸载微信吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101880}, {"id": 348443, "content": "真正明白了现实与理想之前的区别。\n\n生活也参杂着工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428610}, {"id": 348448, "content": "贫穷、节约、分期", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632590}, {"id": 348450, "content": "高强度高速运转的工作，让我变得越来越没有耐心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667356}, {"id": 348452, "content": "被动的充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981010}, {"id": 348456, "content": "没有生活也没有方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667366}, {"id": 348459, "content": "没法静下心来做长期规划，时间过得飞快", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667376}, {"id": 348717, "content": "工作使我快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668018}, {"id": 348740, "content": "周一到周五：工作；周六、周日，为下个周一到周五充电…。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500160}, {"id": 348744, "content": "和没有共同目标的人哪怕只是处于一个空间都觉得太疲惫和恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360023}, {"id": 348492, "content": "渐渐磨淡了生活的激情 失去自我 变成一个忙碌的空壳 两点一线", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039400}, {"id": 348750, "content": "周末听到电话响心就咯噔一下。害怕…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668172}, {"id": 348751, "content": "前路迷茫，无人倾诉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668172}, {"id": 348757, "content": "窗口弹出@就下意识紧张，接电话前必须做好心里建设", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 348504, "content": "平常是机器，只有周末，我才是我", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1504338}, {"id": 348505, "content": "屡屡受挫，却激起了我的征服欲，非要战斗胜利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667449}, {"id": 348763, "content": "在“下一份工作会更好”和“哎其实每个工作都差不多”之间纠结徘徊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668213}, {"id": 348511, "content": "还在接受的过程\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667492}, {"id": 348512, "content": "我需要大量的虚无", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667509}, {"id": 348513, "content": "建筑工程从业者，心情和身体节律随忙季的节律而起伏，肤色也是，和家里的关系也是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327401}, {"id": 348517, "content": "是个好问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598738}, {"id": 348518, "content": "工资深深地影响着我的生活质量和个人愿望，逐渐明白自己有多平凡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667355}, {"id": 348519, "content": "get到了“领导”这个以前非常讨厌的口头禅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529440}, {"id": 352359, "content": "「TGIF」", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681346}, {"id": 348520, "content": "闲了不知道干嘛\n闲多了就有点慌\n没有挂念的休息一天就很幸福", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667575}, {"id": 348783, "content": "通勤时间在既怕睡过站又困得真不开眼中度过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580780}, {"id": 348549, "content": "原来我这么讨厌工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665175}, {"id": 348552, "content": "终于知道睡觉有多么重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626045}, {"id": 348553, "content": "承认废材这件事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555771}, {"id": 348565, "content": "还贷款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1667665}, {"id": 348323, "content": "把朝九晚五当成“一天”，其他时间变成了工作的前奏和尾声", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348324, "content": "Get 了“同事”这种介于朋友和陌生人之间的特殊人际关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 350, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348325, "content": "微信成了生产力工具，看到微信小红点就会紧张一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348583, "content": "开始觉得能坚持做自己喜欢事情的人是真特么牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445495}, {"id": 348588, "content": "逐渐“帅气上班族”化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649868}, {"id": 348596, "content": "通勤时间属于淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182393}, {"id": 349145, "content": "更加仔细和小心，待人接物时更加懂得保持距离。看事情时有了新的视角", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1669793}]}